accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Prints and Printing Slide Collection, Arts Library, Yale University

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Collection consists of color and black and white 35 mm slides of printing techniques and prints worldwide.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: Arranged alphabetically by geographical region or country. Further arranged by individual artist name. Individual artist name sections may be preceded by either or both an anonymous or miscellaneous grouping. Preliminary section on printing techniques (lettering and printed books).
